This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=5016

Overview

Screenshot:
  http://cl.ly/image/1t0W0V3W3E2O/autocdls.gif

The Github repository for the autocdls is available at:
  https://github.com/b4b4r07/vim-autocdls

Usage:
  :Ls {path}
    List the files and directories in {path} like a shell 'ls'.

  In addition, execute ':Ls' automatically after executing ':cd'.
